data.description: Searching for the perfect home with space and a mother-in-law suite? This property features a main level with 3 beds/2bath as well as a separate 2 bedroom/1.5 bath apartment with kitchen on the lower level! That's the potential for two homes in one - with NO HOA! The main level features an open concept floor plan allowing the perfect space for hosting complete with a double sided fireplace. Real hardwoods floors are throughout the entire main level. The spacious owner's suite offers a large walk-in closet as well as a beautiful clawfoot bathtub, double headed shower, and a large double vanity. The lower level (with outside entrance only) boasts a kitchen capable of fitting a full size fridge, has a full sized oven, newly installed cabinetry - plenty of space! The outdoor kitchen has new granite countertops as well as trex decking and screens. Numerous fruit trees including peach, plum, apple and more are planted on the property. Located off I-20, this home is in a great location to access shopping, restaurants, Ft Eisenhower, and I-20!
